               <p>(There were three other indictments against Henry Jolly, one against Phoebe, and one against Mary Ann Jolly, for robbing the prosecutor, who stated his loss at 50<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. or 60<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.)</p>
